Solvay opens U . S . auto parts plant . Solvay Automotive Inc . , a unit of Belgian chemical group Solvay SA , inaugurated on Thursday a new $ 80 million ( 2 . 4 billion Belgian franc ) production facility in Adrian , Michigan , Solvay said in a statement . The unit will make plastic fuel tanks and composite intake manifolds for customers Chrysler and General Motors . - - Nick Antonovics , Brussels Newsroom + 32 2 287 6817 , Fax + 32 2 230 7710 
